regularly checks the status of your website and measures its
"availability"&mdash;a very important non-functional metric. The
blog post [SixNines.io, Your Website Availability Monitor](https://www.yegor256.com/2017/04/25/sixnines.html)
described how you can get a nice looking badge for your website:

